orbit2: ORBit is a high-performance CORBA (Common Object Request Broker
orbit2: Architecture) ORB (object request broker).  It allows programs to
orbit2: send requests and receive replies from other programs, regardless
orbit2: of the locations of the two programs.  CORBA is an architecture
orbit2: that enables communication between program objects, regardless
orbit2: of the programming language they're written in or the operating
orbit2: system they run on.
